title: [Shipshape Overhaul]
description: Coils of rope are piled in the corners of the spacious room.  Several bundles of sailcloth are draped over stacks of sealed wood.  Rectangular windows line the upper walls allowing beams of sunlight to fill the store.  A worn driftwood counter rests along the far wall under a brilliant crimson silk banner depicting the wyvern symbol of Ta'Vaalor.
